Leading some to say that MCP is dead. This is not the end of my talk, so I do not agree that MCP is

00:11:25.619 --> 00:11:32.659
dead. I think that, like most things, there's some truth to the excitement, and there's something to

00:11:32.900 --> 00:11:41.460
the criticism. Since it was the first standard way to add capabilities and tools to your agents,

00:11:42.619 --> 00:11:49.739
people did things with MCP that, in retrospect, in 2026, you certainly wouldn't use MCP for that.

00:11:51.619 --> 00:11:56.859
There were a number of critiques, and I want to step through a few of them and use that to bring

