rebuilding all of this context that you were trying to save by not using MCP, and of course,

00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:33.419
you can only use command line utilities if your agent has access to run commands in the shell,

00:14:33.419 --> 00:14:39.820
and that's not always the case. You might have an agent that you have deliberately not given shell

00:14:39.820 --> 00:14:44.619
